{"tid":574864,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"聽完chef le mon後我竟然⋯","createTime":"2018-02-27T18:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-28T08:12:23.000Z","uid":63704,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"739d5dafbd1070f35493757679ded69b75a4ab3e","tid":574864,"uid":63704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QcvjC8XjxmU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQcvjC8XjxmU&d=MP5r6eUwNfSjSFn0NXIBnzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=9e0d032d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QcvjC8XjxmU</a><br />\n<br />\n謝霆鋒 《有火》<br />\n<br />\n第一次聽呢首歌馬上有個想法，又係一首後資本主義以熱血爲名去榨取你最後一點生產力既歌。「在痛苦中追趕夢」呢一句我真心抱有好大疑問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  乜追夢會覺得痛苦咩？如果追趕得痛苦就未必係你夢想啦，下嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？尤其係chef le mon唱比你聽⋯ 心諗你屋企有返咁上下，加埋你個chok樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，如果你追夢都痛苦我是咪應該節儉小小，保留最後一點自知之名匿返入個龜殼，免得<br />\n連資本主義嘗試榨取我既氣力都曬鳩埋。無奈事情總係會出錯，everything can go wrong will go wrong. <br />\n<br />\n最近係一個好攰既晚上，感覺好多方面都受到錯折。Random左呢首出黎。最初冇太爲意，但聽聽下開始跟個鼓un下un下。呢個感覺相信好多中意聽band sound既朋友都會有呢個經驗。但之後敵不過好奇心，開左個歌詞睇。「但笑著發夢永不知錯」呢句又幾撚中喎，廿鳩幾歲人做左咁多決定，係啱係錯理閪得佢，最緊要呢一刻笑住覺得自己做得啱。叻人跟住自己意願做野，蠢人又係跟住自己意願做 ，啱唔啱，叻唔叻，不用分得那麼細。<br />\n<br />\n最後祝各位巴打「看似冷靜情緒 也有熱血躁動」，共勉之。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efd1f0265006d5e7acc6ecd81d26c2679bebc5f","tid":574864,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"竟然d咩姐到底係"},{"pid":"f0c6d2983484ed636dad918fa1882dcbbf44f47a","tid":574864,"uid":63704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5efd1f0265006d5e7acc6ecd81d26c2679bebc5f","tid":574864,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"竟然d咩姐到底係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:27:46.000Z","msg":"本身對佢d歌從來冇興趣 最後入左playlist <br />\n<br />\nsor 巴打，我今晚無病呻吟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9372cee3279f3bec3add41f73f82e275bb0bcaa","tid":574864,"uid":138138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T18:30:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>竟然d咩姐到底係</blockquote>本身對佢d歌從來冇興趣 最後入左playlist <br />\n<br />\nsor 巴打，我今晚無病呻吟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔緊要  抒發下感受姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正如我都成日聽廢柴 食塞米 扮晒蟹既屎忽鬼"},{"pid":"fc28552e7b5837df694060b323ed0c51bfe8038c","tid":574864,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-28T08:12:23.000Z","msg":"聽歌聽到你d中二病發晒出嚟"}]}